{
  "stem": "4764.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember any of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, look out the window and just look at the scenery and try not to, sort of, run around.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a very obedient child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I must have been, because I never ran out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just sat there looking out the window.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember what I saw, but I remember-- the next scene, I remember very well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was arriving in Budapest, and there was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH] is a-- is, at the station, is a-- instead of a cab, they used to have these horse drawn carriages.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not carriages, but, you know, like they have in Central Park, in New York, where people go for-- but that used to be the mode of transport.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other thing I don't like about trains is the platform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know how they-- you know how the train has to come up to a certain platform, right, and it's got to be higher.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the train's not there, you just see the platform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've never liked that platform-looking thing because there was always-- there was always this thing about trains and deportation and-- and escape in the train.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never liked that-- that-- the view.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When there's-- it's just a platform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see lots of pictures of platforms with no trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the train is there, it looks OK because it looks like it's running into each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When there's no train, only the platform, this looks like you're waiting for something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Screwed up life, eh?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I remember the platform in-- in-- in Brat-- in Czechoslovakia, waiting for the train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I'm going back.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
